title: The Land - Native American flute Stephen Muires shakuhachi
description:
CD with Native American flute music, recorded in 2010 by Stephen Muires.

These recording are free of copyright, and shared without restriction.
Contact email:   
Website of artist:

All mp3 files are 320 kbps.

The Land
(Coyote Oldman Belo Cozad replica, cedar)

(Mark Purtill Anasazi flute in low F#, plastic)

(Shepard 2.4 Shakuhachi, bamboo)

Swirl
(Ken Light PF Waterspirit flute in F#, plastic)

Change
(Little Horse flute, A, cedar)

Upset
(Coyote Oldman flute, alternative tuning, in A, cedar)

Trees and Valley
(Cherokee cedar flute in A)

Hilltop
(Coyote Oldman flute, alternative tuning, in A, cedar)

Vision Quest

Rim
(Mark Purtill Anasazi flute in A, plastic)

Stepping Into the Circle

Stillness
